bio: I'm Giulian, a passionate Full-Stack Developer with a love for creating elegant, efficient, and user-friendly web applications. My journey in tech started with curiosity and has evolved into a fulfilling career where I get to solve problems and build things that make a difference.
When I'm not coding, you can find me exploring new technologies, contributing to open-source projects, or enjoying a good cup of coffee while reading about the latest trends in web development.
